WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.872
Digital is not a side channel anymore — it is part of every

00:00:03.922 --> 00:00:07.795
Porsche customer relationship. You now have the tools to make video updates that

00:00:07.845 --> 00:00:11.415
lift approval of recommended work. You can text professionally without crossing lines.

00:00:11.465 --> 00:00:15.337
You can write emails customers will actually read. And you know which channel

00:00:15.387 --> 00:00:19.260
fits which message. In the next module, you will keep building on that

00:00:19.310 --> 00:00:23.182
foundation. If you'd like to review any of the earlier slides before taking

00:00:23.232 --> 00:00:27.104
the final quiz, click the menu button near the top left of the

00:00:27.154 --> 00:00:31.027
screen. That opens the slide menu, where you can select any completed slide

00:00:31.077 --> 00:00:34.949
to revisit it. When you're ready, click the Final Quiz option at the

00:00:34.999 --> 00:00:38.871
bottom of that same menu to begin. You'll need to score eighty percent

00:00:38.921 --> 00:00:40.078
or higher to pass.
